_sText: It is a jailbreak map. A large octagon, with 5 octagon shaped buildings and an off ground walkway around the perimeter. The center building is a place for people to camp and such, its a two story building with 3 ways to the second floor. Two opposite buildings are cells, with 16 wall mounted cell pod things in each. The other two buildings are medic and gunroom. Gunroom is fenced off, but has multiple ways to get past the fence. The entrance to gunroom is raised off the ground with some boxes to get up. 16 ct spawn points in gunroom.
